1. *Ljubavi* je najveći dar koji možeš da pokloniš nekome. (Love is the greatest gift you can give someone.)

2. On je govorio o svojoj *ljubavi* za nju. (He was speaking about his love for her.)

3. Oni su bili oboje puni *ljubavi*. (They were both full of love.)

4. *Ljubav* je nedostojna patnje. (Love is unworthy of suffering.)

5. Moja *ljubavi* je najvažnija stvar u mom životu. (My love is the most important thing in my life.)

6. Ona je činila stvari iz *ljubavi*. (She was doing things out of love.)

7. On je tražio *ljubav* u svim pogrešnim mestima. (He was looking for love in all the wrong places.)

8. Ona je bila puna *ljubavi* prema njemu. (She was full of love for him.)